column9: 🏞️ Pre-Human - before 200,000 years ago when modern homo sapiens appeared
⛺ Pre-Historic (pre 3000 BCE) - before the invention of writing about at 3,000 BCE
🏛️ Ancient (pre 450) - before decline of Rome at about 450 CE
🏰 Middle Ages (450 - 1500) - before Italian Renaissance at about 1500 CE
⛪ Early Modern (1500 - 1750) - before French Revolution at about 1750 CE
🏭 Late Modern (1750 - 1945) - before living memory at about 1945
⛩️ All time periods ie long history
